        <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.8;">
          <p style="margin-bottom:.4rem;">1. Check your employer has your correct visa subclass on file</p>
          <p style="margin-bottom:.4rem;">2. Provide your TFN if you haven't already</p>
          <p style="margin-bottom:.4rem;">3. Ask payroll to apply the <strong style="color:var(--text);">Working Holiday Maker</strong> tax table</p>
          <p>Under-withheld tax becomes a bill at tax return time — set aside the difference each pay.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

